  "remarks": "Lipetsk Mechanical Plant is a Russian military industry company. It provides weapons to the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation. It manufactured self-propelled tracked chassis for the S-300V4 surface-toair missile systems that were used by the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation during Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
